{"tid":2013174,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「國歌法」殺到埋身啦！！！！","createTime":"2020-05-12T06:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T10:44:03.000Z","uid":283906,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc672907fc375fad7d4ef176d262a4bbe2a964b","tid":2013174,"uid":283906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"政府計劃於本月27日，在立法會恢復二讀辯論《國歌條例草案》及另外9條草案。<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗去信立法會現任內會主席李慧琼，他說本屆立法會會期只餘兩個多月，所有未能在7月立法會會期中止前完成審議的法案，都會在本屆任期完結時失效。政府樂見上星期五召開內會特別會議，終能突破困局，目前有10項政府法案，可適時提交立法會大會恢復二讀辯論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525673-20200512.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525673-20200512.htm&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=0ad84bff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525673-20200512.htm&h=4f9cf55a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525673-20200512.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c263eaa4d4b76d0b4ae55810db7933184f5741d8","tid":2013174,"uid":78211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推呀"},{"pid":"d464028656889b625cc2a4d6e04672ebf5d66bc8","tid":2013174,"uid":283906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"27號！"},{"pid":"47ba0885ba3762c63f6b9a6ecacda34f65b8d6e7","tid":2013174,"uid":283906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:42:44.000Z","msg":"宗仔想上位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cec5177c3c9f031c5965b9206eabc028ca8fe1b","tid":2013174,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as